This paper discusses machine learning models and their susceptibility to adversarial perturbations, which is a common topic in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments conducted in the paper are focused on image classification datasets, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the sample complexity of robust learning, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper mentions the model family and training algorithm, which are topics in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
